54
00:06:20,562 --> 00:06:31,725
IPO race 2026: Bloomberg reports Anthropic is weighing an IPO as early as October 2026  — in parallel with OpenAI's SoftBank loan signal.

55
00:06:31,725 --> 00:06:38,462
Analysts consider it possible that both leading AI labs could go public before the end of 2026.

56
